                <p class="content-description">In addition, travel arrangements provide you with a feeling of security that your travel plans are confirmed and coordinated with your visa application. Apart from flights and lodging, foreign exchange and insurance are also included in travel arrangements. Having the local currency available and knowing you are insured in the event of medical emergencies or trip cancellations makes your travel more convenient. Pre-arranged airport pickup and local transportation saves you time and trouble upon arrival. A detailed travel schedule also makes it easier to pass through customs and immigration because you are able to give a clear indication of your visit if you are interrogated by the immigration officials. In short, proper travel plans not only secure your visa application but also your travel experience as a whole by ensuring you are well-prepared for all that life presents to you.</p>
